# Colang 2.0 — Topic Control Flow

define user ask off topic
  "what is the weather"
  "tell me a joke"
  "write me a poem"
  "what are your personal opinions"

define flow topic control
  user ask off topic
  bot redirect to topic

define bot redirect to topic
  "I'm designed to assist with tasks related to the Secure AI Gateway system. Please ask questions related to security, AI, development, or system administration."
